Dfa

public Dfa(java.lang.String alias,
           java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentSkipListSet<State> states,
           Alphabet alphabet,
           State initialState,
           java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentSkipListSet<State> finalStates)
    throws java.lang.Exception
Constructor for DfaController. This will create an automaton with the given parameters.

Parameters:
alias - Readable name for the automaton.
states - Set of states for this automaton.
alphabet - Alphabet that this automaton will recognize.
initialState - Initial state for this automaton. This state should be included on the states set as well.
finalStates - Final states. These states should be included on the states set as well.
Throws:
java.lang.Exception - Thrown if initialState or the finalStates are not included on the states set.
